response.overview: Watch 4 Recruits fight for their dream of a college bid in front of every single Division 1 Coach in this epic Lacrosse Documentary from All-American, UPenn Division 1 Player, and US Lacrosse H.S. Coach of the Year ALEX WEBER. Featuring exclusive interviews with Top Head Coaches from the biggest Lacrosse Programs in the nation: NOTRE DAME, NORTH CAROLINA, DENVER, MICHIGAN, CORNELL and PENN.
response.tagline: The #1 film in America's fastest growing sport, LACROSSE.
response.title: Committed
